title: South Korea 30 Year bond-Yield
description: South Korea 30 Year Bond Yield was 4.14 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the South Korea 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 4.40 in October of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for South Korea 30Y.
